recamFV3Nu8kES0ph,32,recMlOE0gQr4FBm8h,0,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-at-frosty-faustings-xvii/event/wonderful-world/overview,3rd Lineup,recPSzSF36bmhTpF5,recdgyZSPxiI4Jpq8,True,True,True,5,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/35/35/1733313600000/4wWk7NAOlUS3ocElLw6stw/d8Eryk8ejNeJ1oop-Q74w8AuHn4CUxFuRyli8cS3RKeShzw8IteiV-5pii2kIWiW1CJ6-y-F7J0XzbSAa6a2fPM-aJ-YP6YpUgw1nCJrOLQWOSJkgzzg9KMFWrLDr4yPNy2FiGd19O5Uo4PxvzvmOnAJBIhamdZyqDwUmxU2jaQ/z_R9AEaF6Y6Pa2R6cZXHjtpd94gb1dMVhGpgwkrXUrk,WW,PC,WW - (PC),,thorntheletter,WW%20-%20%28PC%29,2024-10-25T07:22:10.000Z,WanWan,34%,0,2024-12-04T02:42:40.000Z,rec8GAdYl6aqwrQdM,thorntheletter#957944,/admin/general,thorntheletter,0,,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-at-frosty-faustings-xvii/event/wonderful-world/overview,https://vortexgallery.moe/info#WW,0,0,0,3,0.75,a7ae2760,0,0 Hours,thorntheletter,Wonderful World,WanWan,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/35/35/1733313600000/oBFWQKryT6N4FRr3vfV8Lg/1sap_RFEIDOyjnoRsmM0PaVcLCSfX896LWv8RcBN49gH7BSv_aibrXajFFeqsuCzlrEd4toIzxdsY6M4htPFgMYo1Kmhg3xGq_HNG0XZ5xUkdMQz3mR2TbDoJLXxTJRh5OmiLjxUrQLx0h8tcyi-5AuoinDRT0wJ5m5iKamdD4w/KSDaHyZUbIeBIqPKjGKBjOq43Q3HbdQwT3Y3t5Ig3YA,,60/30/10,recamFV3Nu8kES0ph,Double Elimination,2/3,2/3,Timer off (0).,Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,All glitches are to be played through if possible; currently no game breaking glitches or methods of reproducing the meter glitch are known.,"3/5 Games for Losers Finals, 3/5 Games for Winners Finals, 3/5 Games for Grand Finals",Sun. 1/26,,3,3 Hours,"Sun. 1/26, Sat. 1/25, Fri. 1/24, Thurs. 1/23",4,2pm (honestly no preference for days or times so long as it does not conflict with any of our other stuff),thorntheletter,11,,,,,11 / 32,,"Yes, at the very least from me (thorntheletter) but there may be more later.",100,,,recamFV3Nu8kES0ph,,,,,"Vanguard Princess Launcher (for more graphics settings): https://github.com/LlamaMaster/VANGUARD_PRINCESS_LAUNCHER_1.0, put exe and launcher files folder into same directory as game exe, put shortcut in known location. Launch and set exe paths for the game (and LilithPort if use).
button binding script: https://github.com/thorntheletter/buttonbinds, put exe somewhere accessible
 AntiMicroX (backup in case the button binding script has issues with a controller; it is way slower to bind so ideally it is not used but best to have just in case): https://github.com/AntiMicroX/antimicrox install or get portable version, keep (or shortcut) in a known location

optional: Lilithport (lets us save replays): https://github.com/UltiMario/LilithPort-Alpha, download, open, set exe path to game exe and turn saving replays on (Options (O) > Save Replays (R)) (optionally change replay directory). When it comes time for the tournament skip connecting to a server launch through Vanguard Princess Launcher (Play Online), skip connecting to a server (Cancel, bottom right corner button), and launch the game by doing Commands (C) > Start 1P Game (G). 
"
